subject: Breeders' Cup (Horse Race)
Horse Racing
Horses
Kentucky Derby
lead_paragraph: Bob Baffert’s promising 2-year-old Midshipman raced to victory in the Breeders’ Cup Juvenile, establishing himself as an early favorite for the Kentucky Derby next year.
